{"tid":1318973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實琴晚班狗開一半放人入火車站係好混亂，但冇乜片段有紀錄","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:20:42.000Z","uid":42364,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fa58630e49d792476fae28ddbf4c63dcd94f9736","tid":1318973,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"當時個個都想入火車站<br />\n班狗隨機拉人出黎圍毆<br />\n之後起哄<br />\n班狗再分隔<br />\n然後再隨機拉人出黎圍毆<br />\n連準備入閘嘅人都畀狗隨機拉<br />\n冇任何攻擊<br />\n舉高手退緊都隨機捉人出黎打<br />\n<br />\n同時又見到有幾個手足抬住個冇意識嘅女仔入閘<br />\n之後大堂班first aid要AED機<br />\n嗰陣嗰到冇記者少fist aid少資源<br />\n到目前為止都冇見到有片段影到嗰陣嘅情況<br />\n因為過哂去中庭<br />\n<br />\n希望如果大家有/識人有紀錄<br />\n可以公開畀大家睇<br />\n可以嘅盡量blur樣同一啲易認特徵"},{"pid":"b0e89848ca045eae2161f166f8b75eeaa60c4fb6","tid":1318973,"uid":42364,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"嗰個位當時真係好慘烈<br />\n但忽略哂"},{"pid":"d50decea81a35e1e5a9f43afb2cea2f4e039abe1","tid":1318973,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a59b1daca8ec3b0f6152ddb5d072394b31c2766","tid":1318973,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:22:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6de39d35c4134f314673422b0d5d0176da22dbfc","tid":1318973,"uid":18401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee6e80413126231272c59454dc3fb4fc66243ca6","tid":1318973,"uid":129790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e70545597aa70c6bac6720da934f97625866f421","tid":1318973,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"當時應該十點左右"},{"pid":"b064c4da5093a196b9450026597f44a6bea9a72f","tid":1318973,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"港共期待緊死第一個警察或者示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1318968\" data-